  schema:teaches "What it means for a poem to be metrical" , "The difference between meter and rhythm" , "The four metrical systems and why English uses accentual-syllabic" , "How to recognize metrical poetry from non-metrical poetry" , "Why metrical writing is still practiced" ;
  schema:identifier &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/writing/domains/poetry/texts/what-is-metrical-poetry/> .

